Subject: [PATCH] ata: ahci: Disable DIPM if host lacks support
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f7870e8d345cdabfb94bcbdcba6a07e050f8705e
